profile:
The Rental Dept, fine rental furniture & accessories available to stagers, real estate professionals, builders and homeowners alike.
Do you need new furniture and decor accessories to stage your home without the expense of buying new? The Rental Dept offers upscale furniture and accessories for the purpose of home staging.  It's a proven fact that beautifully furnished and staged homes sell faster and for more money. In a competitive market your home needs to stand apart from the others and make a memorable impression. An important part of that first impression is the furniture that potential buyers see the moment they walk through the door. By renting our contemporary furniture and unique accessories your home will instantly get an updated look and increase the appeal of your home, creating an inviting environment where buyers can see themselves living.  
The Rental Dept can help you get the edge over your competition, call today for more details!

The Rental Dept
72 Ditton Dr., unit D, Hamilton
PH#905-818-8961
